Package net.i2p.apache.http.conn.util Description

From Apache HttpClient 4.4.1. For HostnameVerifier. Small modifications to remove additional Apache dependencies. Apache 2.0 license.

Moved to net.i2p.apache.* packages in release 1.8.0 (API 0.9.54).
